Your skin is what you eat! Skincare is important but your diet matters equally (maybe even more when you get older)! Whenever I refrain myself from eating high sugary food, my skin always results in less breakouts and vice versa. I tried to incorporate beauty supplements, food that are rich in antioxidants or cell regeneration into my daily diet since I am in my mid 30s.
